Certainly, it's five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Perfect, Debra. Thank you for providing your details. We will contact you soon to arrange your lessons.

Thank you, Roy. I'm looking forward to it!

You're welcome, Debra. Thank you for choosing Harmony Music School. Have a great day!
